Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 這位美女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵箱地址告訴我唄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去麥當勞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 去嘛去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦 老子是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:41.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 各位 過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:43.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是過得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:45.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:49.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會有一個很棒的派對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時代也有鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家盡情玩樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:01.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就順便抽空收拾掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:02.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 犬夜叉 你到底在想些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:13.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 雖然不知道你掉進了咒泉鄉的哪個溺泉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:18.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你這副樣子 變得還不夠完全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:20.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你聲音跟我很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:31.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是這個樣子比較適合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:32.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蹭我蹭…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:35.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你也很靚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:37.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 叫啥名啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:38.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵箱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…三圍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒法師的後代嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在本大爺面前調戲戈薇 你還真有膽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:52.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位啊 好好相處嘛 對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:54.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達…令…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等下 拉姆 別衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾三搭四 絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金剛槍破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:14.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便到處亂摸 像你這種人絕不饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:19.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子咆哮彈 猛虎高飛車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:38.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 週刊少年SUNDAY創刊50周年紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一同歡聚的絕佳派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:44.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始咯 開始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來把他抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:15.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬 快抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是八寶齊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:23.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…金蟬脫殼術？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:36.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嫩 太嫩了 你還差得遠呢 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:41.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我八寶齊怎麼會被這種小伎倆打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:53.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次總算抓住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付你真是輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:12.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那時間自誇 還不快把胸部遮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你叫我抓的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也選個好點的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被不可愛的女人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你個不知廉恥的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你個暴力女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個變態男
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敢說啊 你個水桶腰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓亂馬聞了這個春眠香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:29.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要聞了一次 不到春天過去是絕對不會醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前把亂馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西你叫我聞我就聞啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 什麼時候醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晚上都在人耳邊咯吱咯吱的 誰都會被吵醒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:44.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就省得我廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地給我聞這春眠香就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:06.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:07.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬 給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住才有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就聞這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你煩死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 一大早的到底在吵什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:21.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我閃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:40.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了 小茜替亂馬聞了春眠香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是悲劇了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:50.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小茜醒來之前 我就和她一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 春眠香？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說那老頭失敗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五寸釘 不需要稻草人偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:26.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 早上那麼吵害我都沒睡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點困呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay 7 days
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the purpose of your visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天道同學真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小茜 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課時間睡覺的話可不是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛子老師要好好教訓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:06.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天道同學她…天道同學她打我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:10.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罕見啊 小茜居然頂撞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春眠香的效果終於出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小茜 就和我一起睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這…這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該我問才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全是按照秘傳書上說的來做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:38.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春眠香是根據秘方所製
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:49.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓每日不停應戰而無暇睡覺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入睡時也可以打鬥的魔法薰香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看了說明再做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你這麼問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:16.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 小茜同學就會一直睡到春天結束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 小茜在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的東西沒了 快去拿些過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 珊璞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:37.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕人就要像僕人一樣利落地幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 右京大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小茜 肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 主人 我現在就去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我引以自豪的親手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西 我才不要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在做夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:12.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能待在心愛的主人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全地…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入了夢境呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什麼時候啊  起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的 這都做的什麼夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬 這是我給你做的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亂啊 也吃一點我親手做的料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多吃不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:01.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分 我本來還覺得只是個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:05.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我當笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用暴力將沉睡的少女喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是一如既往的木訥男啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:39.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來 都是用王子溫柔的吻來喚醒睡美人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就由我來將你喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次飛得真夠遠的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你這是什麼裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:18.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我對小茜同學沒什麼企圖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:24.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這班裡的男生還真是低能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:29.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始沒注意到 原來這本書的下一頁寫了注意事項
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:36.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春眠香是為時刻進行戰鬥的人所制的秘藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一在非危險狀況下使用了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:45.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會激化平時積攢的憤怒而對周圍人亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要特別注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有這樣的副作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 已經開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕緊阻止的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:58.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊追 右京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:00.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:07.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能把球踢過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球抱過來也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:49.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 在情況變得不可收拾之前不阻止她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:54.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃課可是No Good的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:15.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種Bad Student就由我來懲罰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算找到了 夢幻的黃金像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:36.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這麼髒的話 就分辨不出真假了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擦得乾乾淨淨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可真亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜那傢伙出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是被小茜弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒面子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在街上走著走著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一不留神就撞進了工地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:20.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是專程逃課出來和我約會的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 要趕緊找到小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜的話剛才來我們店裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:41.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 慘了 飯店危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:42.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你就不管我們了嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小姑娘真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 來晚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊睡覺一邊還在吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都已經第24碗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真的在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於快出結果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝者是天道茜和畢考克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間只剩30秒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢分明啦 獲勝者是天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:31.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 冠軍天道茜的獎品是由我們八寶齊先生送出的熱吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:39.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算找到了 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 趕緊阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 還是上課時間哦 快回學校去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂七八糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}貓 貓 貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}不要 不要 走開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好啊 右京 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:27.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛子老師 趁現在吸掉她的鬥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩你一個人了 天道茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧 八寶五十元必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你得逞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:50.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太過分了 天道同學是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是幼兒園小朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把天道茜帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的宿敵天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:11.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就讓你嘗嘗地獄的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:16.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 總算老實點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:20.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 就先讓她躺著休息會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓她聽聽能讓心靜下來的音樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:33.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算到了最後的時刻 天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:39.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 在痛苦煎熬中死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來救我的吧 我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁機在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 亂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:03.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要亂馬抱著小茜的話 她就不會繼續惹事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:07.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個世界 你就老老實實地抱著她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說些自作主張的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再離開我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜她在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在做著好夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬 按他們說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一個一個都這麼隨便胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我還沒有分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:43.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬你這傢伙 好大的膽子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷靜一點 良牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 鬼才有空聽你廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好被我懲罰的覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:08.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手吧 為什麼你們兩位總是爭執不休呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別阻攔我們 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是賭上男人尊嚴的勝負之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都請住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要爲了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:20.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都給我住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:28.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 這什麼怪力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管小亂還是良牙竟然都打不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜真的那麼強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是潛在能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再臟的污漬也能洗乾淨的這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是洗衣粉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}注：日語中潛在和洗衣粉的發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:46.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 人一般是無法發揮出自己100%能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在小茜在睡眠狀態中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大限度地發揮出了自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不承認 小茜比我還要強什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死也不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是爭這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:04.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓小茜醒來的話 飯店會被毀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 這種情況下還在發什麼神經啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:22.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:30.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法 只能用這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:42.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 蚊香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來似乎如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:47.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這其實是聞後必醒的夏來香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:48.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏來香？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:52.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣的話應該會醒過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼不早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓小茜聞這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:16.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:18.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是驚人的速度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是小茜的潛在能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:21.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還太嫩了 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:27.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個死老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:31.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下怎麼能對小茜進行正面攻擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:32.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.59,0:22:33.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:36.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這玩意兒這麼弄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 還有這樣的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:42.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 嘴對嘴地讓她吸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹…幹什麼啊 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我久能帶刀更適合做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:51.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:57.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是難看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯店的修理費該向誰收呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:03.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個給我適可…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:05.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體諒我 辮子姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:07.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和我接吻的話再等一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過先來個熱切的擁抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:11.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要和你這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.81,0:23:19.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:26.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:28.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:29.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂分寸的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是光站著看的時候啊 亂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:43.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個男人的話 就趕緊去給小茜一個蘇醒之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:44.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:50.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬君 你莫非是想說你不願意和我女兒接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:54.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:57.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 夏來香到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:23:58.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:06.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我響良牙從沒想過自己會在眾人面前和女性接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:09.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況對方還是睡著的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:12.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為了小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:14.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經顧不上什麼廉恥心了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:19.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜小姐 我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.22,0:24:24.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.91,0:24:27.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是別壞我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:29.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.87,0:24:32.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天道茜的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:33.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能交給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:37.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邪氣是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.66,0:24:38.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.49,0:24:41.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夏來香的副作用 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:46.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有邪念的人聞到的話 邪念就會噴發而出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.96,0:24:47.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:54.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.01,0:24:56.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 快給我恢復理智
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.05,0:24:58.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.87,0:25:01.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫幻戀香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.09,0:25:04.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然幫你忙讓我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:07.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為了這個店 我也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.41,0:25:11.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這副施恩的態度也讓我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.89,0:25:13.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這時候我也別無選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.37,0:25:15.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這個怎麼使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.34,0:25:18.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.29,0:25:22.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.40,0:25:26.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟糕 她又開始發瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:27.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.95,0:25:28.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.63,0:25:35.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸了這個香的人會把所有人看成自己喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:36.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是禁斷之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:37.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.97,0:25:41.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.35,0:25:43.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.30,0:25:47.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 把這香給那些傢伙聞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.31,0:25:48.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在對著誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.47,0:25:50.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.53,0:25:53.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.79,0:25:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.78,0:26:03.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八寶齊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.92,0:26:08.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八寶齊大人 小茜在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.81,0:26:10.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對 我在這裡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.41,0:26:14.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.25,0:26:15.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.87,0:26:20.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的吻來喚醒你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.42,0:26:29.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這個我看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.44,0:26:35.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真會找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.82,0:26:38.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 亂馬 吸進去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.93,0:26:43.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.02,0:26:46.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是變得和這群傢伙一樣該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.35,0:26:47.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.48,0:26:49.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的人已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:52.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在趕緊給小茜一個蘇醒之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.29,0:26:53.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:55.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.19,0:26:57.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻後會有怎樣的後果你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.40,0:26:58.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.92,0:27:01.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻這種東西 一次兩次的又不會掉塊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.87,0:27:06.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個 聞了之後就一定會接吻的魔法薰香
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.09,0:27:10.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在特價含稅3980円 要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.63,0:27:14.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.20,0:27:16.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 先給我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.01,0:27:18.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.37,0:27:19.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.48,0:27:19.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.93,0:27:25.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 我已經忍受不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.33,0:27:29.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不行的 亂馬殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.44,0:27:30.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.43,0:27:36.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 亂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.33,0:27:37.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們看看你男人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.08,0:27:40.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這麼催我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.23,0:27:46.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 這只是一個吻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.65,0:27:50.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一切都是為了讓小茜醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:52.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是使命
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.12,0:28:00.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.86,0:28:01.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.47,0:28:02.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙…煙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.63,0:28:04.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.16,0:28:06.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.67,0:28:08.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙呢 那個小豬形狀的香爐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.38,0:28:13.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子小茜就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.87,0:28:15.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到春天結束就不醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.23,0:28:17.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂馬君 你這傢伙真是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.43,0:28:21.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}這…這怎麼會是我的錯呢 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.45,0:28:22.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 在吵些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.33,0:28:37.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到這點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.23,0:28:42.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 早上了哦 該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.28,0:28:46.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.38,0:28:52.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 好像睡了很久的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.64,0:28:55.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小霞姐姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.98,0:28:58.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.91,0:28:59.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好意思問 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.16,0:29:00.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.15,0:29:03.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.65,0:29:04.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.23,0:29:08.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說你完全醒不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.75,0:29:11.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.06,0:29:12.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.12,0:29:14.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.83,0:29:18.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春眠香是對刺客的殺氣有反應的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.67,0:29:22.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小霞一點殺氣也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.18,0:29:26.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為這樣才做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.58,0:29:31.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這該怎麼辦啊 店都亂七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.20,0:29:36.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢 就讓這些傢伙幫忙收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.11,0:29:54.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.14,0:29:56.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.43,0:30:00.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才做了奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.07,0:30:02.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.26,0:30:04.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了可別笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.08,0:30:09.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夢裡 亂馬一身王子的著裝 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.26,0:30:13.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭…這都什麼夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.29,0:30:15.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.21,0:30:18.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢話就留在做夢時去說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.68,0:30:23.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能和你做那事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.56,0:30:25.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.83,0:30:28.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是個夢 我早就揍死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.84,0:30:30.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少趾高氣揚了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.84,0:30:32.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做那種夢還早了30年
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.53,0:30:34.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是50年
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.07,0:30:36.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敢說啊 你個人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.21,0:30:37.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 水桶腰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.85,0:30:40.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.38,0:30:42.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
